  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency postcss-scss to v1 - autoclosed",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss\">postcss-scss</a> from <code>v0.4.1</code> to <code>v1.0.2</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>postcss/postcss-scss</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"102\">1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/9cebde74ac5687e236b4f2489c14cae163a7d298\"><code>9cebde7</code></a> Release 1.0.2 version</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/98f98feadb10e6740ca52bcb69312dca9c39655b\"><code>98f98fe</code></a> Use PostCSS 6.0.3</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/c1ef3e867cac7055c23f183315cc6359f4e76449\"><code>c1ef3e8</code></a> Update dependencies</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/d0818b893965cdc0a6f194802e451e7cbb3d2cc1\"><code>d0818b8</code></a> Backport escape sequence parsing</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/200f7c43470eef15873024ac0df3792033a802c4\"><code>200f7c4</code></a> Fix indent</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"101\">1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/5e948e81fe32614f4c7d3af93904f473e7e92ae0\"><code>5e948e8</code></a> Release 1.0.1 version</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/0c93ea4cf044178b3a7ce7bc1facf899b0a802d2\"><code>0c93ea4</code></a> Update dependencies</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/81f8130888aeccae5682f3f3e8844024df39a0e5\"><code>81f8130</code></a> Support newline in url()</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/9023a83cdfc4701363873ebe17bc45ecab928d08\"><code>9023a83</code></a> Add ChangeLog header</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"100\">1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/f21242b86baa9ad217ab64462a3f83151db14555\"><code>f21242b</code></a> Release 1.0 version</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/eb82675109ebda6e83ac64dbd85474e45ac0576c\"><code>eb82675</code></a> Use PostCSS 6</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/48f6fbdb393cd0440ad79a7815756531f266c14a\"><code>48f6fbd</code></a> Update dependencies</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/97dba6e108c4be7fb117baa3cf183fe0473b14e2\"><code>97dba6e</code></a> Use babel-preset-env</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/f87894c3d0a59366fb213b91c092e67130cd73c3\"><code>f87894c</code></a> Move test to Jest</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/c2f5237c156d804325ca56b61b28decc3a2cb5be\"><code>c2f5237</code></a> Remove node.js &lt; 4 support</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/bbb2990d6111a670a2008e57444a758ee95fa904\"><code>bbb2990</code></a> Move configs to package.json</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/80068512515726d0b978b536b5c128d5bbe57864\"><code>8006851</code></a> Better yarn usage</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-scss/commit/09f4739b845782defc35ac6d9ca804afe40d60da\"><code>09f4739</code></a> Fix .npmignore</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
